quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  24,51,"Anndu ko woni konngol gom…óin…ìe …ìen si …ìe noddaama faade ka Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on fii yo o √±aawu hakkunde ma…ì…ìe, ko nde …ìe wi'ata: \"Men nanii men …óoftike.\" ∆Åen …óon ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  24,52,"Kala …óoftii…óo Alla e Nulaa…óo Makko on o huli Alla o rentii [e Lepte Makko …óen] haray …ìen …óon ko kam…ìe woni malaa…ìe …ìen"
  24,53,"∆Åe woondiri Alla, e hattirde goondooje ma…ì…ìe, si a yamirii …ìe ma …ìe yaltu sanne. Maaku: \"wata on woondu, …óoftaare no anndaa, pellet, Alla ko humpitii…óo ko golloton"
  24,54,"Maaku: \"∆äoftee Alla …óofto…óon Nulaa…óo on\". Si …ìe huccitii(runtiima) anndu ko fawii mo ko, ko o roondaa kon, no fawii on ko roonda …óon kon, si on …óoftike mo on feeway, fawaaki Nulaa…óo on si wanaa yottinngol …ìanngungol"
  24,55,"Alla Fodii …ìen gom…óin…ìe e moo…óon …ìe golli mo∆¥∆¥i …óin O lontinay …ìe ka leydi wano O lontinirnoo non …ìen adii…ìe …ìe, ma O wee…ìinan …ìe diina ma…ì…ìe ka O welanaa …ìe, ma O wattitan …ìe …ìaawo kulol ma…ì…ìe ngol hoolaare, Yo …ìe rewam wata …ìe sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yeddu…óo …ìaawo …óum haray …ìen …óon ko kam…ìe woni faasiqii…ìe …ìen"
  24,56,"√ëii…ìee e Julde totton Jakka on …óofto…óon kadi Nulaa…óo on, bela jo'o on Yurmete"
  24,57,"Wata a sikku …ìeen yeddu…ìe …ìe laawoto ka leydi, jaa∆¥orde ma…ì…ìe nden ko ka Yiite, pellet, bonii wattnde"